Hellplague:
 
The femme followed him around and watched him work.  He seemed very capable, he turned out to be very handy.
 
"If given time, I bet you could completely resore the ship," she commented with a smile.

rm2kmidi <kraftlos@...> wrote:
Celeron nods, then without warning jumps off the ship, landing on the
panel.  He then bends over and begins to slide it along the ground
toward his little work bench.

When he gets there he leaves the pannel for a moment to check on the
other one in the mold.  It had cooled now, so he began to pull the
molding off of it.  A moment later, he was holding a fresh replacement
pannel.  The color was wrong, but that could be fixed...  (Now on to
the next pannel)


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
